      <title>布林肯称以色列接受停火，哈马斯必须“同意”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/blinken-says-israel-accepts-cease-fire-and-hamas-must-say-yes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周一在特拉维夫对记者表示，以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡已经接受了加沙停火提议，“下一步重要举措是哈马斯表示同意”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/blinken-says-israel-accepts-cease-fire-and-hamas-must-say-yes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 17:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚 Tinubu 乘坐新购飞机前往法国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/nigeria-s-tinubu-heads-for-france-in-newly-acquired-aircraft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布周一乘坐新购置的私人飞机前往法国进行“工作停留”，此举引发批评，因为这个西非国家正经历着生活成本危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/nigeria-s-tinubu-heads-for-france-in-newly-acquired-aircraft</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 17:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚欠国有石油公司 49 亿美元燃料补贴债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/nigeria-owes-state-oil-firm-4-9-billion-fuel-subsidy-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚八月份重新实施的汽油补贴政策，目前已欠其国有石油公司近一半的补贴，相当于今年计划收入的一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/nigeria-owes-state-oil-firm-4-9-billion-fuel-subsidy-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 16:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛领导人的权力游戏在选举前扰乱政局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/lithuanian-leader-s-power-play-roils-politics-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛总统决定阻止执政党候选人进入欧盟委员会，这可能会震动这个波罗的海国家的竞选季，此时距离预计推翻政府的投票仅有两个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/lithuanian-leader-s-power-play-roils-politics-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:28:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚权力斗争加剧，央行陷入争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/libya-power-struggle-builds-as-central-bank-pulled-into-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚央行周一表示，将恢复运营，无视更换行长和董事会的决定，此举可能进一步危及该欧佩克国家敌对政府之间本已脆弱的停火协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/libya-power-struggle-builds-as-central-bank-pulled-into-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪将在俄罗斯入侵后首次访问乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/modi-will-visit-ukraine-for-first-time-since-russia-s-invasion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪定于周五访问基辅，试图平衡与华盛顿和莫斯科的关系，但已排除在调解俄罗斯结束乌克兰战争的角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/modi-will-visit-ukraine-for-first-time-since-russia-s-invasion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗支持的激进组织声称在特拉维夫发动自杀式袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hamas-islamic-jihad-claim-suicide-operation-in-tel-aviv-sunday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的巴勒斯坦组织声称对周日发生在特拉维夫的“自杀式任务”负责，并警告说，只要以色列继续在加沙地带开展军事行动，他们还会采取进一步的类似行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hamas-islamic-jihad-claim-suicide-operation-in-tel-aviv-sunday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>JB Pritzker 出任民主党全国大会主持人，让亿万富翁登上国家舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/dnc-in-chicago-vaults-illinois-governor-jb-pritzker-to-national-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，数千人抵达芝加哥参加民主党全国代表大会，这标志着伊利诺伊州州长 JB Pritzker 多年努力的结果，他希望将这座城市以及他本人提升到全国的聚光灯下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/dnc-in-chicago-vaults-illinois-governor-jb-pritzker-to-national-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚总统将推迟提前投票，局势进一步恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bulgaria-president-to-delay-snap-vote-over-interim-minister-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚总统鲁门·拉德夫意外拒绝批准新临时内阁并表示将推迟提前选举，这导致保加利亚的政治动荡加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bulgaria-president-to-delay-snap-vote-over-interim-minister-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国采取措施缓解因暴乱而加剧的监狱过度拥挤问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/uk-takes-emergency-action-to-ease-prison-crowding-after-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[目前，英国监狱系统已开始接收数百名因最近的骚乱而被起诉的嫌疑人，为此，基尔·斯塔默领导的英国政府批准采取紧急措施，以防止英格兰北部监狱过度拥挤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/uk-takes-emergency-action-to-ease-prison-crowding-after-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:16:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
